{"tid":722733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人] 想搵返個係A33X用50蚊換我40蚊嘅人","createTime":"2018-06-29T18:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T16:44:14.000Z","uid":65342,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9999b8b22bfaa9fcac058228840f6a029e8075c8","tid":722733,"uid":65342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:18:05.000Z","msg":"個日我去完旅行上咗巴士，之後有個男仔拍卡負錢，之後走嚟問我唱錢，佢拎張50蚊紙，我身上得兩張廿蚊，本身諗住用外幣換俾佢，點知佢話唔使就上咗去上層。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢落車先，臨落車笑住做口形同我講唔該，我地互望傻笑咗陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人海茫茫唔知有無機會搵返你，睇下有無機會做個朋友，還返十蚊俾你喇，個故事你明的會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Pygocentrus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPygocentrus&d=EomD8a7AV7nGMz%2BhAuVyjAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e7071efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Pygocentrus</a>"},{"pid":"36a237224eea832460636a282e8ec30a142a86d5","tid":722733,"uid":2419,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:20:23.000Z","msg":"gay故"},{"pid":"248129f0fc906af58a4f5285d55820ed905a98e5","tid":722733,"uid":16120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56264b8a1d2b9e281dfdc660405c3248048d016d","tid":722733,"uid":65342,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36a237224eea832460636a282e8ec30a142a86d5","tid":722733,"uid":2419,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:20:23.000Z","msg":"gay故"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:24:54.000Z","msg":"真人真事 我係絲"},{"pid":"63cbfd28107ba0fe1bb6e4f900f9487e5939ae61","tid":722733,"uid":460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:42:50.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96ba73f5df45937d793603575a00a05a147a962","tid":722733,"uid